{
  "texts": [
    "MathQA requires step by step reasoning involving elementary calculation in order to reach the final answer.",
    "In this study, we take multiple open-source, autoregressive transformer-based LLMs into consideration.",
    "Specifically, Llama 3.1 (Grattafiori et al., 2024), Qwen 3 (Yang et al., 2025), and Mistral (Mistral AI Team, 2023, 2025) model families are selected for analysis.",
    "In each model family, a small-sized model which has less than 10 billion parameters and a medium-sized model which has a parameter size larger than 20 billion is in the scope of our analysis, for the purpose of comparison with respect to model sizes.",
    "For the Llama 3.1 family, Llama-3.1-405B was also used in our experiments."
  ]
}